The logic :



drawing the board :


it shuffle a list of value, and then draw a div with the value in order of the list and go to the next one until there's no more.

each value as an assign svg draw inside the div.


hidding and reaveling :


using the css opacity property to hide the svg.

on click it put the opacity value to 100%.


Checking for pair :


on each click if there's two card with the revealed attribute the system check if the value are the same.

if the value are the same it add a def_revealed attribute, and increment the counter.


Deleting when clicking the 3rd one in a row :


when clicking it checks if there's more than 2 card with the revealed attribute.

if there's more than two it remove the revealed attribute on all card.

and then reasign the reaveled attribute on the current clicked card.

